{"tid":939903,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"維景灣畔連環劈價　兩房戶售708萬年內最低","createTime":"2018-12-13T13:19:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T11:34:20.000Z","uid":174649,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a080d74eb110b1d3c77fc6dddbfd51441d0b6e93","tid":939903,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T13:19:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181213/photo/bkn-20181213201455859-1213_00842_001_01p.jpg?20181213202542\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181213%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181213201455859-1213_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20181213202542&h=6d53c754&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美聯林志堅表示，維景灣畔2座低層C室，實用面積505方呎，兩房間隔，單位7月以890萬港元放盤。業主為求盡快出售物業，於10月初已累減至815萬元，最近受觀塘新盤開售影響，終減價至708萬成交，撇除內部轉讓，售價為屋苑今年的兩房最低位，呎價14,020元。<br />\n<br />\n踏入第4季，該屋苑只錄得9宗成交，購買力大幅萎縮下，買家出價傾向保守。"},{"pid":"7b2068276bf46ad7d355cbf655b4e4be24fbdcc2","tid":939903,"uid":83582,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T13:20:54.000Z","msg":"低層唔計"},{"pid":"f1ddb6935a29b14f595efe7f97f1426b29c46b5b","tid":939903,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T13:25:50.000Z","msg":"買咗觀塘要交訂唔計"},{"pid":"a301e8c77ded7d00fb54182e7b5435744f44f0df","tid":939903,"uid":997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7b2068276bf46ad7d355cbf655b4e4be24fbdcc2","tid":939903,"uid":83582,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T13:20:54.000Z","msg":"低層唔計"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T13:27:04.000Z","msg":"常識黎,唔洗講"},{"pid":"42ce382a76a4207fccab88d7cb83cd69b5f30bdb","tid":939903,"uid":7369,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T13:36:22.000Z","msg":"呎數大過it狗果層唔計"},{"pid":"33e9b4a78a92796718b165abc811792ec6c386ff","tid":939903,"uid":19725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T01:45:41.000Z","msg":"If 6 球就perfect<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=